%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20software%20engineering%20job%20got%20over%203%2C000%20applications.%20Here's%20how%20a%20recruiter%20screened%20out%2098%25%20of%20them%20before%20a%20phone%20call.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223864%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20recruiter%20looking%20at%20candidates%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66476e999fc063e829b24668%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBig%20Tech%20seems%20to%20be%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20smaller%20companies%20to%20hire%20AI%20talent.%3Cp%3EiStock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20software%20engineering%20role%20in%20the%20US%20drew%203%2C367%20applicants.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERecruiter%20Lusely%20Martinez%20used%20an%20application%20tracking%20system%20and%20manual%20checks%20to%20cut%20candidates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThose%20who%20made%20the%20cut%20were%20honest%20and%20understood%20the%20position's%20needs%2C%20Martinez%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Lusely%20Martinez%20and%20her%20team%2050%20days%20to%20fill%20a%20software%20engineering%20role%20for%20a%20global%20tech%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20attracted%203%2C360%20applicants%20and%20seven%20referrals%2C%20she%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7176878384994492416%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20meant%20that%20Martinez%20had%20a%20big%20job%20on%20her%20hands%20to%20filter%20the%20best%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20role%20was%20for%20a%20level%20three%20software%20engineer%2C%20with%20full-stack%20expertise%20and%20knowledge%20of%20specific%20programming%20languages%2C%26quot%3B%20Martinez%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20encourage%20those%20of%20different%20backgrounds%20that%20do%20not%20fit%20all%20the%20criteria%20to%20apply%2C%20there%20are%20spec