ction-2024-amethi-a-bjp-leader-called-him-gandhis-chaprasi-congresss-amethi-pick-replies-5614901%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalled%20%26quot%3BGandhis'%20Chaprasi%26quot%3B%20By%20BJP%20Leader%2C%20Congress's%20Amethi%20Pick%20Says%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmethi%20will%20also%20vote%20today%2C%20with%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%20looking%20to%20win%20back%20the%20seat.%20Mr%20Sharma%2C%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20a%20second-choice%20candidate%20after%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20sister%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20declined%20another%20invitation%20to%20make%20her%20electoral%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-to-contest-lok-sabha-polls-from-raebareli-announces-congress-5577052%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20Files%20Papers%20From%20Raebareli%2C%20Gandhis%20Opt%20Out%20Of%20Amethi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmriti%20Irani%20will%20attempt%20to%20defend%20her%20Amethi%20seat%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspense%20over%20who%20from%20the%20Congress%20would%20contest%20these%20two%20(very)%20high-profile%20seats%20was%20among%20the%20biggest%20headlines%20leading%20up%20to%20this%20phase%20of%20the%20election%2C%20with%20even%20party%20boss%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20leaving%20the%20decision%20up%20to%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fls-polls-rajnath-singh-declares-assets-worth-rs-7-36-cr-5551653%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20is%20also%20on%20the%20ballot%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20contests%20from%20Lucknow%20and%20is%20aiming%20for%20a%20hat-trick%2C%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Ravidas%20Mehrotra%20his%20big%20rival.%20The%20SP%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20and%20has%20been%20backed%20in%20this%20campaign%20by%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaiserganj%20has%20also%20become%20a%20headline%20seat%20as%20it%20was%20the%20constituency%20of%20ex-national%20wrestling%20body%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20dropped%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20under%20heavy%20pressure%20over%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%20against%20him.%20His%20son%2C%20instead%2C%20has%20been%20fielded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flike-my-father-ill-be-there-for-you-brij-bhushan-singhs-son-to-voters-5694314%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELike%20My%20Father%2C%20Will%20Be%20There%20For%20You%3A%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20Son%20To%20Voters%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAway%20from%20UP%2C%20the%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20of%20Mumbai%20are%20also%20voting%20in%20this%20phase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20politics%20has%20seen%20a%20series%20of%20swings%20and%20U-turns%20since%20the%202019%20state%20election%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20BJP%20part%20ways%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20form%20an%20unlikely%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20then%20both%20the%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20have%20gone%20through%20civil%20wars%20and%20seen%20rebel%20factions%20join%20the%20BJP%20(and%20being%20rewarded%20with%20a%20chief%20minister%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20post)%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20controversial%20change%20of%20government%20and%20strengthening%20of%20the%20BJP's%20hand%20for%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai's%20six%20seats%20have%20been%20divided%20amongst%20the%20two%20big%20alliances%20at%20play%20in%20this%20election%20-%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20names%20on%20the%20ballots%20in%20Indian's%20financial%20capital%20include%20Union%20Commerce%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20who%20will%20contest%20from%20Mumbai%20(North)%20against%20the%20Congress'%20Bhushan%20Patil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai's%20North-West%2C%20South-Central%2C%20and%20South%20seats%20will%20see%20grudge%20matches%2C%20with%20the%20original%20Sena%20(led%20by%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20against%20those%20from%20the%20breakaway%20group%20(led%20by%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde).%20North-East%20seat%20will%20be%20a%20BJP%20vs%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20battle%20and%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20vs%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%20North-Central%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20(then)%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena%20swept%20all%20six%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20major%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%20voting%20in%20this%20phase%20are%20Nashik%20and%20Palghar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEknath%20Shinde's%20Sena%20has%20fielded%20sitting%20MP%20Hemant%20Godse%20in%20Nashik%2C%20and%20he%20faces%20Rajabhau%20Waje%20from%20the%20Thackeray%20camp%2C%20while%20Palghar%20sees%20a%20more%20open%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(not%20an%20INDIA%20member)%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20Sena%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20Prakash%20Ambedkar's%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aaghadi%20-%20which%20had%20prolonged%20and%20ultimately%20fruitless%20and%20acrimonious%20talks%20with%20the%20Sena-Congress-NCP%20alliance%20-%20all%20fielding%20candidates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav's%20daughter%2C%20Rohini%20Acharya%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20win%20back%20the%20Saran%20seat%20that%20was%20won%20by%20the%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20in%202009%2C%20in%20the%20first%20election%20after%20it%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flalu-yadavs-daughter-rohini-acharya-up-against-fathers-namesake-in-bihars-saran-lok-sabha-seat-5569890%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELalu%20Yadav's%20Daughter%20Rohini%20Acharya%20Against%20Father's%20Namesake%20In%20Saran%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20though%2C%20it%20has%20been%20held%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Rajiv%20Pratap%20Rudy.%20Another%20high-profile%20contest%20in%20the%20state%20is%20in%20Hajipur%2C%20which%20was%20the%20stronghold%20of%20late%20Union%20Minister%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Paswan's%20son%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20is%20leading%20one%20of%20the%20factions%20of%20the%20LJP%20that%20broke%20up%20after%20his%20death%20and%20has%20allied%20with%20the%20BJP.%20He%20faces%20Shiv%20Chandra%20Ram%2C%20a%20trusted%20aide%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELadakh%2C%20which%20saw%20a%20hunger%20fast%20by%20climate%20activist%20and%20environmental%20reformer%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20in%20March%20over%20demands%20for%20statehood%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20fragile%20Himalayan%20ecology%2C%20sees%20a%20BJP%20vs%20Congress%20fight%20between%20Tashi%20Gyalsan%20and%20Tsering%20Namgyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BK's%20Baramulla%20seat%20is%20also%20voting.%20It%20will%20see%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20and%20National%20Conference%20boss%20Omar%20Abdullah%20looking%20to%20defend%20the%20seat%20won%20by%20Mohammad%20Akbar%20Lone%20in%20the%20last%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-article-370-j-k-faces-existential-threat-omar-abdullah-on-article-370-scrapping-5662643%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BJ%26amp%3BK%20Faces%20Existential%20Threat%26quot%3B%3A%20Omar%20Abdullah%20On%20Article%20370%20Scrapping%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20faces%20Sajjid%20Gani%20Lone%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20People's%20Conference%20and%20Fayaz%20Mir%20of%20the%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20Mehbooba%20Mufti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Con