een%20granted%20bail%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20on%20certain%20conditions%20including%20that%20the%20accused%20should%20work%20with%20the%20traffic%20police%20of%20Yerawada%20for%2015%20days%2C%20accused%20should%20write%20an%20essay%20on%20accident%2C%20should%20get%20treatment%20from%20the%20concerned%20doctor%20to%20help%20him%20quit%20drinking%20and%20should%20take%20psychiatric%20counselling%20and%20submit%20the%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20Prashant%20Patil%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Sunday%2C%20two%20individuals%2C%20including%20a%20young%20woman%2C%20lost%20their%20lives%20after%20a%20luxury%20car%20collided%20with%20their%20motorcycle%20near%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20in%20Pune%2C%20said%20police%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Anis%20Awadhiya%20and%20Ashwini%20Costa.%20The%20tragic%20incident%20occurred%20at%20about%203%3A15%20am.%20The%20driver%20of%20the%20car%2C%20reportedly%20a%20minor%2C%20has%20been%20apprehended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Magar%20of%20Pune%20City%20Police%20confirmed%20that%20the%20juvenile%20has%20been%20apprehended%20and%20his%20father%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20bar%20that%20served%20him%20alcohol%20have%20been%20booked.%20An%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%2C%20and%20an%20investigation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20bike%20rider%20and%20pillion%20rider%20were%20killed%20when%20a%20speeding%20car%20hit%20them%20from%20behind%20in%20the%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20area%20last%20night.%20The%20accused%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20and%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered.%20We%20are%20also%20verifying%20the%20certificates%20to%20ascertain%20the%20accused's%20age%2C%20as%20he%20claims%20to%20be%20a%20minor%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20DCP%20Magar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20charged%20the%20minor%20with%20rash%20and%20negligent%20driving%20and%20causing%20harm%20by%20endangering%20life%20or%20personal%20safety%20under%20IPC%20sections%20304A%2C%20279%2C%20337%2C%20338%2C%20and%20427%2C%20along%20with%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Motor%20Vehicle%20Act%2C%20added%20the%20DCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20juvenile's%20father%20and%20the%20bar%20that%20served%20him%20liquor%20face%20charges%20under%20Sections%2075%20and%2077%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%2C%20said%20the%20city%20police%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20accident%20occurred%20as%20a%20group%20of%20friends%20were%20returning%20home%20on%20their%20motorcycles%20after%20a%20party%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Kalyani%20Nagar.%20At%20the%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20junction%2C%20a%20speeding%20luxury%20car%20struck%20the%20bike%20carrying%20Awadhiya%20and%20Costa%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20fall%20and%20die%20instantly.%20The%20car%20subsequently%20crashed%20into%20roadside%20pavement%20railings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716140700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fo9pv5kdk_pune-porsche-accident_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcounselling-essay-on-car-crash-pune-teen-gets-bail-with-conditions-5700235%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20granted%20bail%20to%20the%20accused%20involved%20in%20a%20recent%20car%20accident%20in%20Pune%2C%20said%20the%20juvenile%20accused's%20advocate%2C%20Prashant%20Patil.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcounselling-essay-on-car-crash-pune-teen-gets-bail-with-conditions-5700235%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcounselling-essay-on-car-crash-pune-teen-gets-bail