portunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wide-ranging%20interview%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20nation%2C%20as%20with%20people%2C%20there%20are%20turning%20points%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20we%20should%20utilise%20that%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlan%20And%20Preparations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20he%20indicated%2C%20is%20already%20on%20the%20job%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20people's%20contribution%2C%20and%20the%20work%20on%20a%20blueprint%20is%20fairly%20advanced.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%20a%20very%20big%20exercise%2C%20a%20mega%20brainstorming.%20I%20have%20been%20doing%20this%20exercise%20for%20so%20long%20that%20some%20officers%20who%20were%20a%20part%20of%20it%20have%20retired.%20We%20have%20taken%20suggestions%20from%20ministers%2C%20secretaries%20and%20experts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20plans%2C%20he%20added%2C%20have%20been%20broken%20up%20into%20achievable%20tranches.%20%26quot%3B%20I%20have%20segregated%20that%20too%20into%2025%20years%2C%205%20years%2C%201%20year%20and%20100%20days%20in%20a%20stage-wise%20manner.%20There'll%20be%20additions%20to%20it%2C%20we%20might%20have%20to%20drop%20a%20thing%20or%20two%20too%2C%20but%20we%20have%20a%20big%20picture%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20visualisation%20of%20the%20country%20at%20the%20age%20of%20100%20started%20while%20planning%20for%2075%20years%20of%20Independence%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20thinking%20of%2075%20years.%20I%20was%20thinking%20of%20100%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BSo%20this%20is%20the%20question%20I%20asked%20wherever%20I%20went.%20I%20asked%20institutes%2C%20'What%20will%20you%20do%20when%20the%20country%20turns%20100%3F%20Where%20will%20your%20institution%20be%E2%80%A6%C2%A0%20RBI%20(Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India)%20had%20a%2090-year-plan.%20I%20said%2C%20'Fine%2C%20what%20will%20you%20do%20when%20the%20country%20turns%20100'%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChannelizing%20The%20Energy%20Of%20Youth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20this%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20is%20to%20think%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20in%20pieces.%20I%20have%20a%20very%20comprehensive%20and%20integrated%20approach.%20Secondly%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20habit%20of%20working%20for%20media%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20enthusiasm%20he%20has%20observed%20among%20the%20young%20people%2C%20he%20said%20he%20has%20even%20devised%20a%20plan%20to%20harness%20it.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20I%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20how%20to%20connect%20the%20youth%2C%20how%20to%20instil%20a%20habit%20of%20dreaming%20big%20in%20them%2C%20and%20how%20to%20bring%20a%20change%20in%20their%20habit%20to%20make%20big%20dreams%20come%20true.%20I%20believe%20these%20efforts%20will%20bring%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20Says%20Victory%20Ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhase%205%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20due%20tomorrow%20and%20two%20more%20phases%20to%20go%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20NDA%20will%20get%20a%20historic%20mandate%20with%20400%20seats%20already%20under%20its%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20exclusive%20interview%2C%20he%20also%20said%20the%20Opposition%20claim%20that%20the%20NDA%20will%20change%20the%20Constitution%20once%20they%20have%20400%20seats%2C%20is%20completely%20off%20the%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20Opposition%20claims%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLinking%20400%20seats%20and%20Constitution%20is%20stupidity.%20The%20issue%20is%20they%20don't%20want%20the%20House%20to%20function%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20things%20first%2C%20there%20are%20already%20400%20seats%2C%20from%202019%20to%202024%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP.%20NDA%20had%20won%20360%20seats%20and%20NDA-plus%20has%20consistently%20been%20above%20400%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20started%20on%20April%2019.%20The%20fifth%20phase%20of%20polling%20will%20take%20place%20on%20tomorrow.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716132840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdafj630c_narendra-modi-ndtv-interview_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-pm-modi-outlines-1-000-year-vision-says-bjp-will-win-historic-mandate-5699223%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20achieve%20big%20then%20think%20big%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20told%20NDTV%2C%20outlining%20how%20thinking%20ahead%20at%20this%20point%20of%20time%20might%20benefit%20India%20a%20thousand%20years%20from%20now.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-pm-modi-outlines-1-000-year-vision-says-bjp-will-win-historic-mandate-5699223%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-pm-modi-outlines-1-000-year-vision-says-bjp-will-win-historic-mandate-5699223%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-pm-modi-outlines-1-000-year-vision-says-bjp-will-win-historic-mandate-5699223%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fatima%20shares%20a%20lovely%20pic%20with%20Manoj%20Bajpayee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716132547000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110251696%2Cimgsize-46304.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffatima-sana-shaikh-drops-a-lovely-photo-with-favourite-co-actor-manoj-bajpayee-from-a-flight-see-inside%2Farticl