Insulted%20Constitution%20Now%20Dancing%20With%20It%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Blasts%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20BJP%20intends%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20NDA%20manages%20to%20cross%20the%20400-seats%20mark%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20told%20NDTV%20that%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20have%20repeatedly%20insulted%20the%20Constitution%20are%20now%20dancing%20with%20the%20Constitution%20on%20their%20heads%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV's%20editor-in-chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20his%20government%20has%20had%20the%20support%20of%20400%20MPs%20since%20the%202019%20election%20results.%20%26quot%3BLinking%20400%20seats%20and%20Constitution%20is%20stupidity.%20The%20issue%20is%20they%20don't%20want%20the%20House%20to%20function%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20main%20Opposition%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20talk%20about%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20ask%2C%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20Congress's%20Constitution.%20Does%20this%20(Gandhi)%20family%20accept%20Congress's%20Constitution%3F%20(Purushottam%20Das)%20Tandon%20became%20Congress%20president%20(in%201950)%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution.%20But%20(Jawaharlal)%20Nehruji%20did%20not%20accept%20this.%20Nehruji%20did%20drama%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20not%20be%20part%20of%20the%20working%20committee.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20to%20remove%20its%20elected%20national%20president%20to%20make%20this%20family%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20then%20referred%20to%20the%201998%20episode%20in%20which%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sitaram%20Kesri%20was%20reportedly%20locked%20in%20a%20room%20to%20prevent%20any%20obstacle%20in%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20elevation%20as%20party%20chief.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20locked%20in%20the%20bathroom%2C%20thrown%20out%20overnight%20and%20Soniaji%20became%20Congress%20president.%20I%20want%20to%20know%20when%20the%20Congress%20functionaries%20of%20today%20became%20the%20party's%20members.%20They%20must%20declare%20to%20the%20country.%20Do%20they%20have%20the%20right%20to%20talk%20about%20Constitution%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20when%20the%20Constitution%20was%20prepared%2C%20what%20was%20written%20was%20for%20the%20present%20and%20the%20future%2C%20but%20India's%20heritage%20was%20showcased%20through%20drawings.%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20drawings%20were%20from%20India's%20heritage%2C%20from%20Ramayana%20to%20Mahabharata%20to%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj.%20Pandit%20Nehru%20dumped%20this.%20The%20Constitution%20published%20later%2C%20he%20had%20removed%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20Pandit%20Nehru%20snipped%20the%20freedom%20of%20expression.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20blow%20to%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20Then%20they%20(Congress)%20attacked%20the%20thought%20behind%20the%20Constitution.%20By%20misusing%20Article%20356%2C%20they%20toppled%20governments%20a%20hundred%20times.%20They%20brought%20Emergency%2C%20put%20Constitution%20into%20the%20dustbin.%20First%20Nehru%20ji%20committed%20this%20sin%2C%20then%20Indira%20ji%20and%20then%20Rajiv%20ji%20came.%20Rajiv%20ji%20was%20bringing%20a%20law%20to%20control%20the%20media%2C%20he%20threw%20away%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20Shah%20Bano%20judgment%20and%20amended%20the%20Constitution%20for%20vote%20bank%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20then%20referred%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20act%20of%20tearing%20up%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20and%20demanding%20that%20a%20UPA%20government%20ordinance%20that%20sought%20to%20overturn%20a%20rule%20that%20disqualifies%20convicted%20MPs%20and%20MLAs%20must%20be%20%26quot%3Btorn%20and%20thrown%20out%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20talking%20about%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20targeted%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20patriarch%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20over%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20fodder%20scam%20case.%20%26quot%3BThose%20jailed%20for%20stealing%20fodder%20and%20are%20out%20on%20health%20grounds%20are%20talking%20about%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20shattered%20the%20spirit%20of%20Constitution...%20they%20tore%20the%20draft%20of%20Women%20Reservation%20Bill%20inside%20Parliament.%20Those%20who%20severely%20insulted%20the%20Constitution%20are%20now%20dancing%20with%20the%20Constitution%20on%20their%20heads.%20They%20are%20lying%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716131820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F12dfgsso_pm-modi-exclusive_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-ndtv-exclusive-those-who-insulted-constitution-now-dancing-with-it-pm-blasts-congress-5698270%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Countering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%20that%20the%20BJP%20intends%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20NDA%20manages%20to%20cross%20the%20400-seats%20mark%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20NDTV%20that%20those%20who%20insulted%20the%20Constitution%20are%20now%20dancing%20with%20it%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-ndtv-exclusive-those-who-insulted-constitution-now-dancing-with-it-pm-blasts-congress-5698270%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-ndtv-exclusive-those-who-insulted-constitution-now-dancing-with-it-pm-blasts-congress-5698270%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.