-4fe0-a833-242b5fc4409e%5C%22%3EWe%20get%20to%20connect%20as%20a%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20practice%20important%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-skills-that-will-make-you-more-likable-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20politely%20ordering%20what%20they'd%20like%2C%20being%20respectful%20of%20fellow%20restaurantgoers'%20experiences%2C%20noticing%20and%20appreciating%20the%20wait%20staff's%20hard%20work%2C%20and%20saying%20thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20part%20of%20all%20though%2C%20is%20the%20connection%20time%20we%20get.%20At%20home%2C%20we%20make%20an%20effort%20to%20do%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-whole-foods-prepared-family-meals-which-to-skip%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20together%2C%20but%20so%20often%2C%20it%20doesn't%20go%20the%20way%20we%20hoped.%20Instead%20of%20having%20connection%20time%2C%20we%20end%20up%20becoming%20the%20server%20of%20our%20kids'%20own%20personal%20restaurant%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20them%20another%20drink%20or%20making%20a%20sandwich%20for%20them%20when%20they%20hate%20the%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20tiny%20table%20means%20the%20kids%20can%20too%20easily%20bug%20each%20other%2C%20so%20we%20also%20end%20up%20breaking%20up%20fights%20most%20nights.%20But%20at%20a%20restaurant%2C%20someone%20else%20is%20doing%20the%20serving%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20cleaning%2C%20and%20we%20get%20to%20do%20the%20fun%20parts%3A%20talking%20about%20our%20day%2C%20playing%20cards%20at%20the%20table%20while%20we%20wait%2C%20and%20encouraging%20them%20to%20try%20a%20fun%20new%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229afdcd78-c304-4ae4-9349-26e23295f4e8%5C%22%3EWe%20choose%20where%20to%20go%20with%20our%20kids%20in%20mind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20hard%20stuff%2C%20the%20good%20parts%20make%20it%20worth%20it.%20And%20even%20the%20hard%20parts%20can%20be%20made%20easier%20by%20choosing%20our%20location%20wisely.%20Breweries%2C%20wineries%2C%20and%20cider%20places%20are%20surprisingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-says-breweries-better-than-playgrounds-for-families-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreat%20fits%20for%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20often%20have%20a%20casual%20atmosphere%20and%20backyards%20(which%20means%20space%20for%20kids%20to%20run%20around).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20local%20cider%20place%20in%20warmer%20weather%20has%20a%20huge%20field%20where%20we%20can%20fly%20a%20kite%2C%20kick%20a%20ball%20around%2C%20and%20just%20generally%20get%20our%20wiggles%20out%20as%20a%20family%20before%20settling%20down%20to%20enjoy%20the%20meal%20together.%20This%20is%20a%20huge%20contrast%20to%20home%2C%20where%20we%20are%20frantically%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20meal%20on%20the%20table%20that%20suits%20everyone's%20tastes%20and%20meets%20basic%20nutritional%20requirements.%20The%20grownups%20in%20the%20family%20arrive%20at%20the%20table%20stressed%20out%2C%20and%20the%20kids%20arrive%20at%20the%20table%20asking%20what's%20for%20dinner%20and%20often%20complaining%20that%20it's%20not%20their%20favorite%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20be%20ignoring%20the%20major%20privilege%20in%20this%20if%20I%20didn't%20point%20out%20that%20we%20are%20lucky%20to%20be%20able%20to%20dine%20out%20as%20a%20family%20sometimes.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20we%20budget%20and%20cook%20our%20meals%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%20We%20often%20opt%20to%20save%20money%20by%20limiting%20packaged%20snacks%20and%20making%20muffins%20and%20cookies%20from%20scratch%20so%20it's%20cheaper%20and%20lasts%20longer%20as%20well.%20We're%20not%20able%20to%20dine%20out%20as%20frequently%20as%20we%20might%20like%2C%20but%20maybe%20that's%20why%20we%20appreciate%20it%20all%20the%20more%20when%20we%20do%20get%20to%20dine%20out%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20keep%20the%20kids%20on%20their%20best%20restaurant%20behavior%20(and%20I%20may%20leave%20with%20juice%20spilled%20on%20my%20clothes)%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20it's%20worth%20it.%20Everyone%20gets%20to%20order%20what%20they%20want%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20that's%20just%20fries%20and%20dessert.%20We%20all%20get%20to%20enjoy%20each%20other's%20company.%20And%20the%20adults%20get%20to%20have%20a%20meal%20they%20really%20love%20that%20they%20didn't%20have%20to%20cook.%20Then%2C%20we%20get%20to%20walk%20away%20together%20as%20a%20family%2C%20feeling%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20connected%20%E2%80%94%20and%20without%20washing%20a%20single%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdining-out-with-kids-hard-fosters-connection-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716130681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644dd80f27898f532d7f81d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdining-out-with-kids-hard-fosters-connection-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Going%20out%20for%20dinner%20with%20our%20three%20kids%20all%20under%20the%20age%20of%2010%20can%20be%20chaotic.%20But%20it%20forces%20all%20of%20us%20to%20connect%20and%20enjoy%20time%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Katharine%20Reid)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdining-out-with-kids-hard-fosters-connection-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bureaucracy%20Needs%20To%20Change%2C%20Promotions%20Cannot%20Be%20Target%3A%20PM%20Modi%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChanges%20in%20training%2C%20recruitment%20and%20a%20citizen-centric%20governance%20are%20the%20salient%20changes%20that%20have%20been%20brought%20about%20in%20the%20labyrinthine%20bureaucracy%2C%20underlined%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EPehli%20baat%20ye%20hai%2C%20ek%20toh%20training%20sabse%20badi%20cheez%20hai%2C%20recruitment%20process%20bahut%20badi%20cheez%20hai%2C%20aur%20maine%20ispe%20bada%20bal%20diya%20hai.%20Training%20institutions%20ko%20humne%20poori%20tarah%20badal%20diya%20hai.%20Technology%20ka%20bharpoor%20upyog%20hamare%20har%20level%20pe%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20first%20thing%20is%20that%20training%20is%20the%20biggest%20thing%2C%20recruitment%20process%20is%20a%20very%20big%20thing%2C%20and%20I%20have%20given%20a%20lot%20of%20emphasis%20on%20it.%20We%20have%20brought%20about%20a%20big%20change%20in%20training%20institutions.%20And%20we%20are%20giving%20technology%20a%20lot%20of%20focus)%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAb%20recruitment%20main%20bhi%20maine%20lower%20level%20pe%20jo%20interview%20the%20woh%20samapt%20kar%20diye%20hain.%20Woh%20brashtachar%20ka%20adda%20ban%20gaya%20tha.%20Gareeb%20aadmi%20ko%20loota%20jaata%20tha.%20Ab%20woh%20merit%20ke%20aadhaar%20pe%20computer%20tay%20karta%20hai.%20Samay%20bhi%20bach%20jaata%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Now%20in%20recruitment%20too%2C%20I%20have%20finished%20the%20lower-level%20interviews%20in%20bureaucracy.%20It%20had%20become%20a%20den%20of%20corruption.%20The%20poor%20man%20was%20being%20looted.%20Now%20the%20computer%20decides%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20merit.%20Time%20is%20also%20saved)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%2073%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20integrated%20approach%20towards%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-explains-why-he-believes-bjp-will-get-historic-mandate-5694244%5C%22%3Eseeking%20re-election%20for%20a%20third%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20his%20personal%20philosophy%20is%20%26quot%3BP2G2%26quot%3B%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bpro-people%20good%20governance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20saw%20infrastructure%20was%20only%20on%20paper.%20I%20started%20reviewing.%20%3Cem%3EKuch%20hamara%20mindset%2C%20kuch%20hamari%20bureaucracy%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Some%20of%20it%20was%20our%20attitude%20and%20some%20our%20bureaucracy)%2C%26quot%3B%20bemoaned%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%2C%20who%20says%20the%20country%20will%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20his%20third%20term%2C%20spelt%20out%20the%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-mega-exclusive-when-scope-scale-and-speed-meet-skill-pm-modis-recipe-for-success-5693189%5C%22%3Efour-S'%20mantra%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20country%20to%20achieve%20big%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20scope%20should%20be%20very%20big%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20in%20parts%2C%20and%20the%20second%20thing%20is%20scale%2C%20which%20should%20also%20be%20large.%20The%20speed%20should%20be%20in%20sync%20with%20these%20two.%20So%2C%20scope%2C%20scale%20and%20speed%2C%20and%20then%20there%20should%20be%20skill.%20If%20we%20can%20get%20these%20four%20things%20together%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20we%20achieve%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20who%20has%20set%20a%20mammoth%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20this%20time%20and%20with%20help%20from%20allies%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20cross%20400%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvoking%20the%20legacy%20of%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20the%20first%20Home%20Minister%20of%20the%20country%20made%20some%20efforts%20and%20had%20he%20lived%20long%20enough%20%26quot%3Bour%20government%20machinery%20would%20have%20been%20better%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20officer%20should%20know%20what%20is%20the%20purpose%20of%20his%20job.%20It%20cannot%20be%20limited%20to%20when%20is%20the%20next%20promotion%20or%20when%20will%20I%20get%20a%20better%20department%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevery-bill-mentions-global-standards-pm-modi-on-plan-to-make-india-better-5695813%5C%22%3Ecabinet%20note%20related%20to%20a%20Bill%20now%20comes%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20global%20standards%20report%20so%20that%20the%20legislation%20can%20be%20matched%20with%20the%20best%20practices%20worldwide%2C%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20days%2C%20a%20tradition%20has%20started%20in%20my%20cabinet.%20Whenever%20a%20Bill%20to%20be%20introduced%20in%20Parliament%20comes%20before%20the%20cabinet%2C%20a%20global%20standards%20note%20comes%20with%20it.%20This%20note%20mentions%20which%20country%20is%20performing%20the%20best%20in%20that%20particular%20field%2C%20what%20are%20the%20rules%20there%20and%20how%20we%20can%20achieve%20that.%20So%2C%20we%20have%20to%20match%20every%20cabinet%20note%20with%20global%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20a%20habit%20for%20the%20bureaucracy%20now.%20Just%20saying%20our%20(plan)%20is%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world%20is%20not%20enough.%20Say%20who%20is%20doing%20the%20best%20in%20world%20and%20where%20we%20are%20and%20how%20we%20can%20get%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20marathon%20six-week%20general%20election%2C%20which%20ends%20on%20June%201.%20Four%20phases%20are%20over.%20Three%20more%20remain.%20The%20votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETune%20in%20today%20at%208%20pm%20to%20watch%20the%20interview%2C%20which%20will%20be%20aired%20across%20the%20NDTV%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716130680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fncj165ds_modi-inter-1200-_625x300_19_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbureaucracy-ne