perate%20in%20California.%20Companies%20like%20Royal%20Caribbean%20International%20and%20Norweigan%20Cruise%20Line%20will%20need%20to%20make%20the%20price%20of%20taxes%2C%20port%20fees%2C%20and%20other%20charges%20clear%20to%20customers%20up%20front%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftravel%2F2024%2F05%2F15%2Fcruise-prices-transparency-taxes-port-fees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20image%20of%20Princess%20Cruises'%20Sun%20Princess%20cruise%20ship%20arriving%20into%20White%20Bay%20terminal%20on%20March%2021%2C%202020%20in%20Sydney%2C%20Australia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecb823ecb92e00192536e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Princess%20Cruises'%20ship.%20%3Cp%3EJames%20D.%20Morgan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Carnival%20Corp.%20representative%20told%20the%20outlet%20it%20would%20follow%20guidelines%20set%20out%20by%20the%20%26quot%3BHonest%20Pricing%20Law.%26quot%3B%20Carnival%20Corp.%20is%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20brands%20like%20Carnival%20Cruise%20Line%2C%20Princess%20Cruises%2C%20and%20Holland%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20is%20a%20California%20state%20law%2C%20we%20are%20making%20this%20change%20nationwide%20to%20ensure%20our%20advertised%20pricing%20is%20consistent%20no%20matter%20where%20guests%20shop%20for%20our%20cruise%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20representative%20said%20that%20from%20now%20on%2C%20the%20full%20advertised%20cost%20would%20include%20extra%20charges%20previously%20%26quot%3Bitemized%20separately%20for%20consumer%20awareness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorweigan%20Cruise%20Lines%20is%20still%20determining%20their%20next%20steps%2C%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Royal%20Caribbean%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.travelandleisure.com%2Fcruise-lines-may-soon-have-to-disclose-taxes-and-port-fees-in-upfront-price-here-s-why-8649469%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETravel%20%2B%20Leisure%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20guests%20can%20expect%20to%20see%20extra%20fees%20included%20in%20the%20overall%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuests%20booking%20with%20Royal%20Caribbean%20International%20and%20Celebrity%20Cruises%20will%20now%20see%20pricing%20that%20is%20inclusive%20of%20their%20selected%20cruise%20fare%20and%20all%20required%20taxes%20and%20fees%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20supporting%20our%20travel%20partners%20across%20the%20country%20ahead%20of%20this%20upcoming%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22serenade%20of%20the%20seas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658f00dcab6f2ebb11f7c786%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Caribbean%20cruise%20ship.%20%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Caribbean%20International%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Carnival%20Corp.%2C%20Royal%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20Norwegian%20Cruise%20Line%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20California%20attorney%20general's%20press%20release%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BHonest%20Pricing%20Law%26quot%3B%20comes%20as%20the%20Biden%20administration%20continues%20to%20address%20hidden%20fees%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bjunk%20fees.%26quot%3B%20The%20Biden%20administration%20first%20announced%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-democrats-are-joining-in-on-bidens-fight-against-junk-fees-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efight%20against%20hidden%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October