-are-close-recession-proof-you-can-get-1759440%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecession-proof%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20may%20be%20due%20to%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flipstick-index-explained-how-makeup-sales-could-forecast-recession-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lipstick%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20theory%20that%20consumers%20continue%20to%20spend%20on%20lower-priced%20luxuries%2C%20like%20salon%20services%20and%20beauty%20products%2C%20even%20during%20economic%20downturns%20and%20recessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20you%20%3Cem%3Eare%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplanning%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20a%20pedicure%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20choosing%20a%20trustworthy%20salon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20salon%20owners%20said%20are%20red%20flags%20to%20look%20out%20for%20when%20getting%20a%20pedicure%20at%20a%20new%20salon.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a7b36cf-1a10-4990-8326-ce38f2b464f3%5C%22%3ESalons%20with%20jetted%20tubs%20may%20not%20be%20thoroughly%20disinfected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERona%20Villamore%20Falls%2C%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrenchiesnails.com%2Flocation%2Fga-braselton%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrenchies%20Modern%20Nail%20Care%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Braselton%2C%20Georgia%2C%20cautions%20against%20getting%20a%20pedicure%20at%20a%20salon%20with%20jetted%20tubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20tubs%20can%20be%20relaxing%2C%20water%20jets%20are%20really%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffootandankle-usa.com%2Fwomens-foot-health%2Fwhat-to-look-for-in-a-safe-nail-salon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficult%20to%20clean%20and%20disinfect%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20to%20fully%20disinfect%20a%20jetted%20tub%20system%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20to%20do%20it%20in%20between%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26qu