0clients%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BPorous%20implements%20can%20carry%20germs%20and%20bacteria%20and%20should%20really%20only%20be%20used%20once.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20if%20you're%20getting%20a%20pedicure%20and%20manicure%20at%20the%20same%20appointment%2C%20nail%20technicians%20should%20also%20use%20separate%20tools%20for%20your%20hands%20and%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c9ee51d-95d5-4cb8-9d78-eb6cbe931ad4%5C%22%3ENail%20technicians%20not%20wearing%20proper%20gear%20can%20be%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20too%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Lana%20Kars%2C%20CEO%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Frussian_nails_nyc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20Nails%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20your%20nail%20technician%20should%20follow%20specific%20practices%20for%20proper%20hygiene%2C%20like%20wearing%20disposable%20face%20masks%20and%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKars%20said%20a%20proper%20technician%20may%20also%20wear%20a%20disposable%20gown%20and%20hat.%20All%20of%20these%20wearables%20should%20be%20disposed%20of%20after%20each%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20helps%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20bacteria%20and%20contaminants%20that%20could%20compromise%20the%20health%20and%20safety%20of%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f34ecd9-d7fb-48f9-9c58-b28813a562c4%5C%22%3EUncovered%20pedicure%20chairs%20may%20not%20be%20the%20cleanest%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKars%20told%20BI%20that%20salons%20should%20cover%20pedicure%20chairs%20with%20disposable%20materials%20to%20prioritize%20good%20hygiene.%20Disposable%20sheets%20or%20covers%20can%20be%20quickly%20tossed%20and%20replaced%20when%20rotating%20clients%20in%20and%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20disposable%20sheets%20demonstrates%20to%20clients%20that%20the%20salon%20prioritizes%20cleanliness%20and%20hygiene%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%2215