ing%20surfaces%20used%20to%20provide%20services%20to%20multiple%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20cases%2C%20salon%20staff%20should%20be%20using%20hospital-grade%20disinfectants%20to%20properly%20clean%20their%20workspaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-bad-pedicure-signs-from-salon-owners-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716128281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663cf1d3b4abc992e8c75c4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-bad-pedicure-signs-from-salon-owners-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20jacuzzi%20tubs%20with%20jets%20to%20uncovered%20chairs%2C%20these%20are%20the%20signs%20it%20may%20be%20time%20to%20get%20a%20pedicure%20at%20a%20new%20salon%2C%20according%20to%20salon%20owners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(%20Alyssa%20Towns%20Swantkoski)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fred-flags-bad-pedicure-signs-from-salon-owners-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Which%20Team%20Will%20Finish%202nd%20In%20IPL%202024%20If%20RR%20vs%20KKR%20Game%20Is%20Washed%20Out%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERain%20has%20interrupted%20the%20proceedings%20for%20the%20last%20game%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20between%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20(RR)%20and%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20in%20Guwahati.%20Toss%20was%20delayed%20due%20to%20rain%20with%20RR%20needing%20a%20win%20to%20finish%20in%20the%20top%20two%2C%20which%20will%20give%20them%20two%20chances%20to%20reach%20the%20IPL%202024%20final.%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20defeated%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%20in%20the%20first%20game%20on%20Sunday%20and%20provisionally%20occupy%20the%20second%20spot%20in%20the%20points%20table.%2