m%20from%20the%20starting%20point%20and%20is%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20around%2010%2C000%20ft.%20We%20stayed%20overnight%20at%20a%20campsite%20in%20Ghangharia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20serves%20as%20the%20base%20camp%20for%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298559%2Fbest-jungle-camps-wildlife-safaris-india-for-nature-lovers-travel-long-weekend%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20stay%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eateries%20and%20scenic%20views%2C%20making%20it%20an%20ideal%20place%20to%20rest%20and%20recharge%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20hike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Himani%20and%20Sagar%20Patel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350346%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHimani%20and%20Sagar%20Patel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDate%203%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20woke%20up%20early%20the%20next%20morning%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F302828%2Fbest-must-take-winter-treks-in-himalayas-uttarakhand-views-adventure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20started%20our%20trek%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fa%3EValley%20of%20Flowers%20which%20was%20around%204%20km.%20We%20then%20entered%20the%20Valley%20which%20is%206-7%20km%20long%20and%20ends%20with%20a%20glacier%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20shared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20there%20are%20no%20eateries%20inside%20the%20park%20and%20you%20will%20have%20to%20carry%20your%20own%20food.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20packed%20our%20lunch%20and%20ate%20it%20with%20the%20best%20views%20of%20the%20valley%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Himani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%204%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20trekked%20from%20Ghangaria%20to%20Hemkund%20Sahib%2C%20which%20is%20a%20steep%20climb%20but%20worth%20the%20effort.%20At%20the%20top%2C%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20Gurudwara%20and%20the%20serene%20lake.%20Hemkund%20Sahib%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20Gurudwara%20at%204%2C329%20m.%20We%20had%20a%20delicious%20meal%20at%20the%20Langar%20and%20then%20trekked%20back%20down%20to%20Ghangaria%20to%20stay%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%205%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20started%20our%20journey%20back%20from%20Ghangaria%20to%20Govindghat%2C%20which%20took%20about%205%20hours.%20After%20lunch%20in%20Govindghat%2C%20we%20drove%20back%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20stayed%20overnight%20at%20the%20local%20guest%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20you%20carry%20all%20your%20medicines%2C%20a%20raincoat%20in%20the%20monsoons%20and%20ample%20amount%20of%20drinking%20water%20before%20you%20go%20on%20the%20trek.%20Once%20you%20are