ed%20me%2C%20he%20told%20me%20that%20I%20deserved%20this.%20I%20heard%20the%20same%20thing%20everywhere%20that%20I%20deserved%20all%20the%20abuse%20because%20of%20my%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20changed%20for%20her%20when%20she%20moved%20to%20Kerala%20in%20Class%2010%2C%20away%20from%20abuse%20and%20a%20city%20where%20no%20one%20knew%20what%20her%20mother%20did%20several%20years%20ago.%20However%2C%20the%20trauma%20of%20the%20first%2014%20years%20of%20her%20life%20led%20to%20many%20difficulties%20including%20her%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20light%20in%20the%20tunnel%20appeared%20for%20her%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20newspaper%20cutting%20about%20Shweta%20Katti%2C%20who%20became%20the%20first%20girl%20from%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273849%2Fhero-smarajit-jana-durbar-collective-helps-kolkata-sex-worker-get-rights%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20red-light%20district%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20secure%20an%20international%20scholarship%20and%20study%20abroad%20at%20Bard%20College%20in%20New%20York.%20Shweta%20asked%20Sandhya%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Robin%2C%20who%20simply%20asked%20her%20to%20catch%20the%20first%20train%20and%20come%20to%20Kranti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20provides%20shelter%2C%20education%2C%20support%20and%20opportunities%20for%20girls%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2021.%20The%20NGO%20has%20its%20own%20school%20with%20six%20teachers.%20Learn%20more%20about%20how%20Kranti%20turned%20her%20life%20around%2C%20along%20with%2027%20others%3A%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC65hOi5LavV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC65hOi5LavV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campa