r%20friends%20over%20in%202018.%20My%20mentor%20and%20the%20nursery%20owner%20conducted%20soil%20tests%20and%20assessed%20the%20climate%20conditions%20in%20Bhopal.%20They%20also%20visited%20other%20farms%20growing%20citrus%20and%20mango.%20After%20evaluating%20the%20area%2C%20they%20suggested%20that%20a%20garden%20could%20thrive%20in%20Bhopal.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20identified%20specific%20avocado%20varieties%20that%20would%20be%20suitable%20for%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20while%20India%20lacks%20high-quality%20avocados%20and%20specific%20varieties%2C%20Israel%20has%20excellent%20rootstocks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20import%20these%20rootstocks%20from%20Israel%20and%20began%20planning%20his%20first%20consignment%2C%20which%20took%20place%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20import%20process%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20lengthy%2C%20complicated%2C%20and%20full%20of%20regulations%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20adhere%20to.%20In%202019%2C%20I%20struggled%20with%20the%20import%20procedure%2C%20causing%20my%20consignment%20to%20be%20delayed%20until%202020%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20went%20to%20Israel%20to%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-4-1715775552-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350093%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20went%20to%20Israel%20to%20learn%20the%20ins%20and%20outs%20of%20avocado%20farming.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20struck%2C%20and%20both%20India%20and%20Israel%20went%20into%20lockdown.%20This%20resulted%20in%20yet%20another%20delay%20of%20one%20year%20for%20my%20consignment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20in%202021%2C%20I%20received%20my%20first%20shipment%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289888%2Fharshit-godha-bhopal-grows-avocado-nursery-farming-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavocado%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Israel%2C%20which%20I%20planted%20in%20my%20own%20orchards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20was%20able%20to%20grow%20this%20batch%20of%20avocados%20in%20a%20polyhouse%20nursery%20the%20same%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20have%20not%20made%20the%20fruit%20commercial%20yet%2C%20the%20yield%20was%20shared%20among%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20I%20planted%20the%20avocado%20plants%2C%20they%20were%20kept%20in%20the%20nursery%20until%202023.%20Finally%2C%20in%20March%202023%2C%20I%20planted%20them%20in%20the%20fields.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20first%20year%20the%20crop%20will%20be%20commercially%20viable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20now%20sells%20avocado%20plants%20all%20over%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20says%20that%20he%20uses%20Israeli%20technology%20to%20irrigate%20his%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20employ%20advanced%20techniques%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20control%20water%20distribution%20precisely%20to%20the%20root%20zone%20of%20each%20plant.%20Instead%20of%20using%20flood%20irrigation%2C%20which%20wastes%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20water%2C%20we%20ensure%20that%20each%20plant%20receives%20the%20exact%20amount%20of%20water%20and%20fertiliser%20it%20needs%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20topography%20of%20the%20orchard%2C%20you%20will%20have%20an%20even%20distribution%20of%20water%20for%20each%20and%20every%20plan%2C%20he%20stresses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETips%20for%20new%20urban%20farmers%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20planting%20avocados%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20keep%20a%20few%20things%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20says%20that%20you%20need%20a%20reliable%20water%20source%20or%20should%20practise%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20especially%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20hot%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20regions%20like%20the%20Northeast%2C%20natural%20rainwater%20is%20usually%20sufficient.%20For%20other%20areas%20like%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20or%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20a%20dependable%20water%20source%20is%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20consideration%20is%20choosing%20the%20right%20variety%20of%20avocado%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CI%20offer%20a%20100%25%20buy-back%20guarantee%2C%20ensuring%20that%20my%20customers%20won%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20problems%20selling%20their%20produce.%20I%20source%20the%20plants%20from%20Israel%2C%20where%20extensive%20research%20has%20been%20conducted%20on%20avocados%20over%20the%20last%2060%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocad