st%3F%20These%20extra%20moments%20could%20be%20crucial%2C%20shaping%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20food%20we%E2%80%99re%20putting%20into%20our%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPackaged%20food%20has%20become%20integral%20to%20our%20lives%2C%20whether%20we%20like%20it%20or%20not.%20Therefore%2C%20making%20conscious%20decisions%20to%20opt%20for%20packaged%20foods%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20pose%20additional%20risks%20is%20essential.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20step%2C%20but%20it%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20our%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20reports%20have%20emphasised%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20carefully%20reading%20food%20labels.%20The%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20released%20dietary%20guidelines%20for%20Indians%20on%20May%208%2C%20cautioning%20that%20the%20information%20provided%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348030%2Fmdh-everest-sambhar-masala-fssai-guidelines-food-safety-ethylene-oxide-fish-curry-masala-singapore-hong-kong%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epackaged%20food%20labels%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20often%20be%20misleading.%20%E2%80%9CHealth%20claims%20on%20packaged%20food%20are%20designed%20to%20catch%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20attention%20and%20convince%20them%20that%20the%20product%20is%20healthy.%20Always%20read%20food%20label%20information%20to%20know%20about%20the%20contents%20inside%20the%20pack%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20guidelines%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20fooled%20by%20labels%20like%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98no%20sugar%20added%E2%80%99.%20One%20man%20who%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20decode%20these%20food%20labels%20and%20teach%20Indians%20how%20to%20read%20them%20is%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20aka%20%E2%80%98foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20this%2032-year-old%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20charge%20in%20promoting%20health%20literacy%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%20before%20making%20purchases.%20Through%20his%20Instagram%20page%2C%20he%20has%20gathered%20a%20following%20of%20over%202.2%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20left%20behind%20a%20lucrative%20Rs%202%20crore%20job%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20this%20certified%20health%20coach%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spark%20a%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndians%20are%20educated%20but%20not%20health%20literate.%20I%E2%80%99m%20therefore%20focusing%20on%20health%20literacy%2C%20with%20my%20major%20target%20being%20children.%20You%20should%20develop%20healthy%20habits%20in%20children%20from%20day%20one%20and%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20junk%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20developing%20health%20issues%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHolding%20large%20FMCG%20conglomerates%20accountable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%2090s%20Kolkata%2C%20Revant%20had%20a%20regular%20childhood%2C%20which%20included%20biscuits%2C%20packaged%20foods%2C%20and%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita.%20The%20young%20boy%20was%20then%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20the%20food%20he%20consumed%2C%20like%20millions%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Revant%20wants%20Indians%20to%20learn%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350079%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERevant%20wants%20Indians%20to%20learn%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20slowly%20learnt%20the%20importance%20of%20nutrition%20over%20the%20second%20decade%20of%20his%20life%2C%20which%20he%20spent%20largely%20in%20the%20US.%20Revant%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20for%20his%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20finance%20and%20management%20in%202011.%20It%20was%20also%20the%20time%20that%20he%20started%20taking%20an%20interest%20in%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347926%2Fcerelac-sugar-nestle-babies-infants-health-nutrition-report-meal-plan-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20food%20and%20nutrition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20eventually%20got%20cemented%20with%20a%20health%20coach%20certification%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20started%20reading%20food%20labels%20carefully%20during%20his%20grocery%20store%20runs.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20eat%20healthy%20and%20started%20paying%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20ingredient%20list.%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20most%20companies%20are%20saying%20something%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20pack%2C%20while%20the%20back%20states%20a%20different%20story.%20I%20slowly%20learnt%20about%20the%20ingredients%20like%20the%20emulsifiers%2C%20colours%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20angered%20when%20he%20realised%20that%20while%20the%20company%20states%20that%20the%20product%20is