%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-3-1715250701-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-3-1715250701-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-3-1715250701-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-3-1715250701-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Tree%20Fern%20is%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20species%20and%20was%20once%20the%20food%20of%20dinosaurs%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaturvedi%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20the%20job%20is%20tough%2C%20Chaturvedi%20has%20a%20stellar%20team%20backing%20him.%20One%20of%20his%20junior%20research%20fellows%20and%20%E2%80%9Cbrilliant%20minds%E2%80%9D%2C%20Manoj%20Singh%2C%20shares%20the%20intricate%20process%20they%20follow%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276600%2Fkerala-man-converts-rubber-plantation-into-mini-forest-medicinal-fruit-plants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econserve%20these%20plant%20species%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20identify%20the%20plants%20based%20on%20their%20family%20and%20genus%2C%20then%20proceed%20to%20collect%20their%20specimens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20factors%20play%20spoilsport%20to%20this%20%E2%80%94%20illegal%20trade%2C%20growth%20of%20invasive%20species%2C%20and%20wildlife%20feasting%20on%20the%20fallen%20fruits%20and%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20birds%20eat%20these%20seeds%20and%20fruits%2C%20it%20disturbs%20the%20natural%20regeneration%20of%20the%20plant.%20There%20is%20no%20chance%20of%20a%20new%20crop.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20and%20Chaturvedi%20lead%20the%20team%20to%20collect%20these%20fruits%20and%20seeds%20and%20take%20them%20back%20to%20the%20centre%20where%20they%20conduct%20experiments%20to%20cultivate%20these%20plants%20through%20vegetative%20propagation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20terrain%2C%20weather%20and%20climate%20are%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CEspecially%20when%2C%20after%20restoration%2C%20we%20proceed%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273494%2Fabdul-kareem-inspiring-hero-who-grew-a-forest-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erehabilitate%20the%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%20their%20natural%20environments.%20While%20these%20altitudes%20are%20conducive%20for%20their%20growth%2C%20it%20is%20a%20tough%20terrain%20for%20us%20to%20access.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20adds%20that%20they%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20plant%20species%20after%20thorough%20research%20through%20Vedic%20literature%20as%20well%20as%20the%20IUCN%20lists.%20Once%20they%20demarcate%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20plants%20thrive%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20care%20not%20to%20publicise%20it%20too%20much%20%E2%80%94%20they%20take%20the%20GPS%20coordinates%20of%20the%20place%20and%20in%20the%20months%20that%20follow%2C%20conduct%20studies%20on%20the%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20plant%20species%20conserved%20is%20the%20Himalayan%20Gentian%20(%3Cem%3EGentiana%20Kurroo)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20striking%20blue-coloured%20flower%2C%20that%20has%20highly%20medicinal%20roots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20it%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20excessive%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F171244%2Fkarnataka-farmer-forest-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover-exploitation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaturvedi%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20plant%E2%80%99s%20